claim: Frederick Trump emigrated to Puerto Rico.
premise_source_doc_sentence: As head of the Privatization Committee he was in charge of the implementation of the government 's privatization policy , which entailed the disposition and sale of several major government-owned assets and dependencies , including , the Puerto Rico Telephone Company , the Puerto Rico Maritime Shipping Authority  (  Navieras  )  and several government-owned hotel properties , centers for diagnostic treatment and hospitals .
